Dragos Industrial Cybersecurity Ecosystem
Asset discovery and compromise assessment; threat hunting and detection; forensics, automated workflows, and incident response. The Dragos Ecosystem provides powerful capabilities for all of these. 














Asset Discovery & Compromise Assessment






Dragos Platform
On-premise Software



Asset Discovery
Today's industrial control systems are complex, and our platform automates the process of asset discovery and analysis; you can't manage what you can't measure.




Dragos Intelligence
Global Threat Context



Risk Prioritization
Rich global threat context enables accurate understanding and prioritization of vulnerabilities




Dragos Threat Ops
24x7x365 Expert Services



Compromise Assessment Service
Our compromise assessment service introduces expert analysis to ramp infrastructure protection exponentially.







Threat Detection & Proactive Hunts






Dragos Platform
On-premise Software



Automated Threat Detection
We use multiple detection techniques—signature-based, baselining, anomaly detection, and industry-specific behavior analytics—to automate threat discovery.




Dragos Intelligence
Global Threat Context



Full Threat Context
Analyzing both known and new threats allows for refined behavior analytics, ensuring comprehensive detection capabilities. We also provide strategic intelligence reports.




Dragos Threat Ops
24x7x365 Expert Services



Threat Hunt Service
Our threat operations hunt service proactively looks for new and previously unseen attacks. If it's out there, we will find it.







Visualization & Response






Dragos Platform
On-premise Software



Forensics & Compliance
We provide powerful, interactive threat investigation capabilities along with automated incident response workflows to amplify remediation efforts.




Dragos Intelligence
Global Threat Context



Risk Prioritization
A rich global threat context broadens and accelerates risk identification, enabling appropriate prioritization and remediation of incidents.




Dragos Threat Ops
24x7x365 Expert Services



Incident Response Service
Our incident response service employs industry-leading expertise and process knowledge to further remediation efforts.











Dragos Industrial Security Components







A | Dragos Platform
Time is of the essence. Our software codifies our knowledge and experience, delivering an intelligent, orchestrated, and automated approach to to asset protection, threat detection, analysis, and response. It listens, it understands, it learns, and it evolves.


B | Dragos Intelligence
A single person or company can’t know everything. Our global threat intelligence contextualizes individual findings and combines them with global threat information to augment our platform and cybersecurity experts—yours and ours. Now you can more accurately discern and validate indicators of compromise.


C | Dragos Threat Operations
In critical situations, contingency plans are crucial. We're here to help. From compromise assessment to threat hunting, to incident response, our experience with the world's most sophisticated and complex networks yields a new level of context, control, and confidence.









